      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://MainStreetMarketingMachinesiPadBonus.com/blog/?p=72</guid>
      <description>&lt;br/&gt;See How MSMM Helps You Set Up Your Lead Page Having bought and registered your domain name with Godaddy.com or any other registrar of your choice you are now ready to create a great looking lead page in order to &amp;#8230; &lt;a href="http://MainStreetMarketingMachinesiPadBonus.com/blog/index.php/set-up-your-lead-page/"&gt;Continue reading &lt;span class="meta-nav"&gt;&amp;#8594;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/main-street-marketing-machines-review-best-bonus-/Main_Street_Marketing_Machines_Review__BEST_Bonus_-MSMM_Training-_Set_Up_Your_Lead_Page.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<br/><div class="tweetmeme_button" style="float: right; margin-left: 10px;">
			<a href="http://api.tweetmeme.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2FMainStreetMarketingMachinesiPadBonus.com%2Fblog%2Findex.php%2Fset-up-your-lead-page%2F"><br />
				<img src="http://api.tweetmeme.com/imagebutton.gif?url=http%3A%2F%2FMainStreetMarketingMachinesiPadBonus.com%2Fblog%2Findex.php%2Fset-up-your-lead-page%2F&amp;style=normal&amp;b=2" height="61" width="50" title="MSMM Training: Set Up Your Lead Page" alt="MSMM Training: Set Up Your Lead Page" /><br />
			</a>
		</div>
<h1>See How MSMM Helps You Set Up Your Lead Page</h1>
<p><a href="http://MainStreetMarketingMachinesiPadBonus.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/tg4.png"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-107" title="MSMM Training: Set Up Your Lead Page" src="http://MainStreetMarketingMachinesiPadBonus.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/tg4-300x157.png" alt="MSMM Training: Set Up Your Lead Page" width="300" height="157" /></a>Having bought and registered your domain name with <a href="http://www.godaddy.com">Godaddy.com</a> or any other registrar of your choice you are now ready to create a great looking lead page in order to start attracting traffic and creating leads for your prospective clients.</p>
<p>Let me just remind you that this series of articles is just an overview of the things you are taught by Mike Koenigs and his team in the <a href="http://www.mainstreetmarketingmachinesipadbonus.com/default.aspx?ref=bpmsmm">Main Street marketing Machines</a> (<a href="http://www.mainstreetmarketingmachinesipadbonus.com/default.aspx?ref=bpmsmm">MSMM</a>) course.  Mike is a great guy and knowing the industry well has created a number of tools that help you achieve your goals.<br />
One of these tools is <a href="http://www.TrafficGeyser.com/cmd.php?af=27873">Traffic Geyser</a> and this is the one you will need to use in order to create great looking lead pages.  It supports an unlimited number of profiles and has a large number of great looking templates for you to work with.<br />
Choosing your template is the first thing you need to do.  There is a list inside <a href="http://www.TrafficGeyser.com/cmd.php?af=27873">Traffic Geyser</a> with thumbnails next to them and you can choose which one you like best.  I would suggest you choose a relatively simple one because it has been proven that the simpler lead in pages are the most converting.  Having chosen your template you are now ready to create your page.  When creating your lead page make sure you choose a keyword rich page name, it is very important that you do so.  Page name is very important to ranking and so is the title the page is going to display, so choose wisely.  Let me give you a piece of advice here, when you are writing all your copy and deciding on the titles etc please do it offline in a text editor.  Save the content and then begin populating your page, you would not want your browser crashing just before you have finished writing a great five hundred word article straight into one of the available text boxes and losing all your work.  It would be a shame don’t you think?  Anyway, once you have put in all your text, set up the colors, fonts etc on the page you can save it and go to the next step which is creating a video to put on your lead page, people love video, so it is necessary to do so.  You might think it is difficult but wait until the next article and you will read the techniques Mike teaches you in <a href="http://www.mainstreetmarketingmachinesipadbonus.com/default.aspx?ref=bpmsmm">MSMM</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
