      <description>&lt;br/&gt;The MSMM system Mike Koenigs and his team have develop is all about generating leads from the internet for Main Street businesses and here is how they propose you go about it after you have chosen your niche. &lt;a href="http://MainStreetMarketingMachinesiPadBonus.com/blog/index.php/create-value-and-give-it-to-people-for-free/"&gt;Continue reading &lt;span class="meta-nav"&gt;&amp;#8594;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/main-street-marketing-machines-review-best-bonus-/Main_Street_Marketing_Machines_Review__BEST_Bonus_-MSMM_Training-_Create_Value_And_Give_It_To_People_For_FREE.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<br/><div class="tweetmeme_button" style="float: right; margin-left: 10px;">
			<a href="http://api.tweetmeme.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2FMainStreetMarketingMachinesiPadBonus.com%2Fblog%2Findex.php%2Fcreate-value-and-give-it-to-people-for-free%2F"><br />
				<img src="http://api.tweetmeme.com/imagebutton.gif?url=http%3A%2F%2FMainStreetMarketingMachinesiPadBonus.com%2Fblog%2Findex.php%2Fcreate-value-and-give-it-to-people-for-free%2F&amp;style=normal&amp;b=2" height="61" width="50" title="MSMM Training: Create Value And Give It To People For FREE!" alt="MSMM Training: Create Value And Give It To People For FREE!" /><br />
