      <description>&lt;br/&gt;Main Street Marketing Machines (MSMM) by Mike Koenigs has been a great help for my business. Before I had a chance to learn all the information Mike has put into this course I had no idea of what I could do if I had the right tools. &lt;a href="http://MainStreetMarketingMachinesiPadBonus.com/blog/index.php/getting-clients-and-making-money-from-main-street-marketing/"&gt;Continue reading &lt;span class="meta-nav"&gt;&amp;#8594;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/main-street-marketing-machines-review-best-bonus-/Main_Street_Marketing_Machines_Review__BEST_Bonus_-Getting_clients_and_making_money_from_Main_Street_Marketing.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
